 } } \right]$$<br><br>Let P be the plane containing all those ($$\alpha$$, $$\beta$$, $$\gamma$$) for which the above system of linear equations is consistent, and D be the square of the distance of the point (0, 1, 0) from the plane P.<br><br>The value of | M | is _________.

